  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Wider impacts of COVID-19 on health monitoring tool
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">National monitoring tool that brings together metrics to assess the wider impacts of coronavirus (COVID-19) on health.</p>

  </div>
</div>

