      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The monitoring tool collates metrics across a range of wider impacts to provide stakeholders with a single point of access. This will enable stakeholders to:</p>

<ul>
  <li>monitor changes over time or against an agreed point in time</li>
  <li>make timely, informed decisions</li>
  <li>intervene early to mitigate against poor outcomes</li>
  <li>understand the wider context on population health</li>
</ul>

<p>The tool will be updated weekly and may include the addition of new metrics as they become available or data updates to metrics already included in the tool.</p>

</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

